# 000-docs/

This directory follows the Intent Solutions Document Filing Standard v4.3:
`NNN-CC-ABCD-<title>-<date>.md`

Examples:
- `001-DR-RFC-<title>-<date>.md` — Design RFC
- `002-AT-DECR-<title>-<date>.md` — Architectural Decision Record
- `003-AT-ARCH-<title>-<date>.md` — Architecture document
- `004-AA-AACR-<title>-<date>.md` — After-Action Compliance Report

Empty at v0.1.0 scaffolding. Populated as decisions land.

Source of truth: `~/000-projects/intent-eval-platform/intent-eval-lab/000-docs/` for cross-cutting platform decisions (DR-035 etc.). This repo's `000-docs/` is reserved for dashboard-specific Decision Records.
